<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814488>
    dc:description "Figures 63-68. Theridion musivum Simon (63-64), female from Corsica (63), female guarding egg-sac from Sardinia (64). T. pinicola Simon from Corsica (65-67), male (65-66), copulating pair (67). T. semitinctum Simon from Northern Italy, female vulva, dorsal view (68)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814488/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3814490>
    dc:description "Figures 69-75. Theridion pinicola Simon from Corse, Forêt de Bonifatu. Male palp, retrolateral (69), ventral (70), prolateral view (71). Epigynum/vulva, ventral (72, 74), dorsal view (73, 75). 69-71 and 72-75 drawn at same scale. Scale lines: 0.20 (69-71) and 0.10 mm (72-75)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3814490/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

